org.apache.poi.ddf

Class EscherChildAnchorRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherRecord
      • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherChildAnchorRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public class EscherChildAnchorRecord
extends EscherRecord
    The escher child achor record is used to specify the position of a shape under an existing group. The first level of shape records use a EscherClientAnchor record instead.(escher child achor记录用于指定形状在现有组下的位置。第一级形状记录使用土方ClientAnchor记录。)
    See Also:
